commit 6ad0ad2bf8a67e27d1f9d006a1dabb0e1c360cc3 upstream.

Skylake suffers from RSB underflow speculation issues; report this
vulnerability and it's mitigation (spectre_v2=ibrs).

  [jpoimboe: cleanups, eibrs]

